name: uniVote
body:
### Welcome to uniVote! This is the official document web page for our uniVote project for Software Engineering, CSCE 4444. This will primarily function as the place to download the code, view specifics about the implementation, and to have a graphical "README" if you will. Below is some code to clone the project: (Although it is private) ``` $ cd your_directory_of_choice $ git clone https://github.com/ksibod/uniVote.git ``` If you're using the GitHub for Mac or PC, simply sync your repository through the GUI app. ### More stuff here later... We can add content here if we want.
